  <source>University Hospital, Clermont-Ferrand</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparing a pharmacokinetic model of a short sevoflurane sedation in burn ICU patients with
      control ICU patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective clinical study in ICU with sedated ventilated patients with sevoflurane with the
      AnaConda® system, establishing pharmacokinetic model of sevoflurane and its metabolites
      (hydroxyfluroisopropanol, fluoride) comparing burn and non burn ICU patients
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
